data.description: Come see this spacious corner lot no step ranch 3 bedroom (or 2 bedroom and garage), 1 bathroom home in the heart of Lockport. Walk in to vaulted living room ceilings. Kitchen has granite counter tops and plenty of counter and cabinet space.  Garage was transformed into 3rd bedroom, but can easily transition back to a garage. Fully fenced backyard for privacy. Roof replaced in 2016.  Call to view today!
